{"id":"13582ba8-7228-4a61-aa78-a44ba328995c","title":"1547: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"d92d525f-1414-49a0-b6d9-caf96e63fe68","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, ... [1547].","standoffProperties":[{"id":"780e72f2-cdc8-426d-b288-b249a28a9910","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"90c6bf77-4159-49e3-a142-74fb5d81f3b7","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"da6e749d-03e5-4cae-bf3c-1dadcc62b5b8","type":"codex/time-reference","start":16,"end":19,"value":"8cd154e0-c397-48ad-b09b-34bd561309d9","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"e0aff65a-53ba-47d7-a005-a5ddca096f8a","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"0bbf2c6b-7737-4d51-b80e-1661fbc416ad","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3a2d9ffe-15fe-418f-be89-b485685b21f2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"b058c99c-cb46-4458-be52-b172d5851e57","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"74b7d4a4-0d41-4838-8f72-85b20b412964","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":1,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"8e433dcc-e996-4466-8efd-00494766a2dc","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"c5c3c1b8-727a-438b-a638-1ae8be071260","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"b5e4b2f1-25e9-4e81-9a52-649c0f122a84","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I have written to thee concerning thy taking a wife, and I told thee of three girls whose names had been mentioned to me here. One is a daughter of Alamanno de\u0027 Medici, another the daughter of Domenico Gugni and the third a daughter of Cherubin Fortini. None of them are known to me,\u00A0and therefore I can tell thee neither good nor bad\u00A0of them, nor can I advise thee to take one rather\u00A0than another. If, however, Michele Guicciardini is\u00A0willing to trouble himself over the matter he would be able to find out what sort of people they are and inform us. He could do the same if I hear of any more. Therefore beg him to do this for my sake, and salute him in my name. As to buying a house, it appears to me that this will be necessary before\u00A0thou canst marry, because your present house is not large enough. So if thou writest to me about this\u00A0matter see that thy letter be written so that I can read it: that is, if thou desirest me to answer and tell thee my views. Messer Giovan Francesco also\u00A0might be able to advise thee well in these matters, for he is a man of years and experience. Commend me to him. But above all seek counsel from God,\u00A0for this is a serious step in life. I would remind\u00A0thee that there should be always at least ten years difference between the age of husband and wife;\u00A0and have a care that she be healthy as well as good. I have no more to say.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"9c35b865-03f3-43b5-8f92-775860122593","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"43b35776-ad54-42bb-8f82-b34facd31df0","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":12,"end":12,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"cf747b2b-9ab8-4539-99b4-87dfe98123b5","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":46,"end":48,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id